      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HELLO HILDA (5) is racing well without winning, recording three minors on end, the latest hitting the ground running with a fast early sectional but finishing in the minors again when third (19.95) over 350m at Goulburn. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Well-placed to take this out. GOLFER GIRL (1) was below best last time when seventh but three back was a Mix winner in quick time at Nowra. Key player on best and worth another try. HOODWINKED (3) resumed from a break finishing sixth (23.56) at Richmond in a Grade 5. Will be much improved. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Key runner on best form. ROSCOE CONKLIN (4) is a last-start placegetter here at this trip - worth considering.",
